msgctxt "297\t357"
msgid "Come on!"
msgstr "¡Adelante!"

msgctxt "369\t575"
msgid "Leading the Tojo is a heavy cross to bear.\\nIt's time you learn just how heavy."
msgstr "Te mostraré el verdadero peso\\nde cargar el emblema del Clan Tojo."

msgctxt "594\t688"
msgid "We'll see about that, Kiryu!"
msgstr "¡Vamos, Kiryu!"

